Eman Mohammed Summary

Eman Mohammed, based in United Arab Emirates, is currently a senior editor at Al ittihad newspaper. Eman Mohammed brings experience from previous roles at AFP, Abu Dhabi Tourism & Culture Authority and Abu Dhabi Authority for Culture and Heritage. Eman Mohammed holds a Bachelor's degree in Journalism @ United Arab Emirates University. With a robust skill set that includes Editing, Social Media, Public Relations, Media Relations, Marketing Communications and more.
